.data-labels {
  font-size: 12px;
  text-anchor: middle;
  font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.histogram {
  font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;
}
.histogram .axis path,
.histogram .legends path,
.histogram .axis line,
.histogram .legends line {
  fill: none;
  shape-rendering: crispEdges;
}
.histogram .axis text,
.histogram .legends text {
  font-size: 11px;
  stroke: transparent;
  stroke-width: 0;
}
.histogram .legends text {
  font-size: 12px;
  text-anchor: middle;
  stroke: transparent;
  stroke-width: 0;
}
.histogram .column {
  fill: transparent;
}
